name: From the Imagination of the Guild Keeper

metadata.name: Astro Dragon Knight
metadata.description: The Astro Dragon Knight are fierce protectors of the Planet Neptune and has been since the planet was created.  Their flair and smart ass mouths have gained them quite the following across the galaxy.  There's even a comic book series that has been running for almost 4000 years and had been a top seller across 15 of the 32 planets in our solar system.
